Key Match Events: Tanner Bibee pitched 6.0 innings, gave up two hits, allowed one earned run, struck out six hitters, and walked three batters.
Bibee escaped a bases-loaded jam in the sixth inning, giving up only one run.
Kyle Manzardo went 3-for-4, including an extra-base hit.
Brayan Rocchio hit a two-run homer in the top of the seventh inning.
Rocchio worked a walk with the bases loaded in the eighth inning, earning another RBI.
